WEBVTT

00:10.600 --> 00:12.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

01:06.540 --> 01:08.000
[The Eternal Fragrance]

01:08.000 --> 01:11.980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

01:12.020 --> 01:15.140
[Episode 9]

01:51.520 --> 01:54.340
Using such expensive travel talismans just to transport wine?

01:57.310 --> 01:59.940
His Majesty's Duantu Nectar is finally here.

02:01.030 --> 02:02.940
Why send wine all this way?

02:05.880 --> 02:08.140
How can the Mid-Autumn Festival be without wine?

02:09.440 --> 02:10.290
- Mid-Autumn Festival? - Mid-Autumn Festival?

02:16.430 --> 02:17.130
Smells good, right?

02:18.320 --> 02:19.460
So many mooncakes.

02:20.320 --> 02:20.970
Lifei!

02:22.390 --> 02:24.460
Changyue specially picked these from Qingqiu.

02:24.480 --> 02:25.850
They are tailored to local flavors.

02:26.270 --> 02:29.130
Five-nut filling made with vanilla, nectar, wild jujube,

02:29.590 --> 02:31.410
and dried grass stems.

02:31.480 --> 02:33.250
Once Ye and Tongzhou get back from shopping,

02:33.270 --> 02:34.250
we can dig in.

02:34.900 --> 02:36.130
My master was stingy back then.

02:36.150 --> 02:37.740
He never wanted to spend money buying me mooncakes.

02:37.870 --> 02:39.410
Always fobbed me off with potato cakes

02:39.430 --> 02:40.970
and radish slices.

02:41.520 --> 02:41.900
Here.

02:42.110 --> 02:43.020
What should I grab for you?

02:43.040 --> 02:43.500
That one.

02:43.520 --> 02:44.020
That one.

02:44.110 --> 02:44.740
- This one? - Yeah.

03:27.520 --> 03:28.410
Put it in?

03:30.360 --> 03:30.810
A bit more.

03:30.830 --> 03:31.500
More?

03:32.200 --> 03:32.620
Enough?

03:32.800 --> 03:33.220
That's enough.

03:33.240 --> 03:33.620
Okay.

03:36.150 --> 03:39.370
If only Shanhua were here.

03:41.960 --> 03:42.780
Smells so good.

03:42.920 --> 03:44.180
This one.

03:52.520 --> 03:53.130
Changyue.

03:54.040 --> 03:54.650
This one.

04:09.760 --> 04:10.370
What are you doing?

04:19.390 --> 04:20.370
Are you missing Lu?

04:28.910 --> 04:29.860
I get it.

04:33.390 --> 04:35.100
Festivals always make you miss your loved ones.

04:36.680 --> 04:37.770
I miss my master too.

04:40.200 --> 04:41.770
That old man would probably

04:42.030 --> 04:43.890
be humming a little tune if he were here.

04:46.520 --> 04:49.060
They'll all be here someday.

04:59.710 --> 05:00.300
For sure.

05:02.980 --> 05:05.250
But we should still enjoy ourselves this time.

05:06.790 --> 05:08.100
Let's go make mooncakes.

05:09.230 --> 05:09.740
Come on.

05:10.980 --> 05:13.370
Let's go. Come on.

05:21.980 --> 05:22.570
Hurry.

05:24.660 --> 05:25.060
Here.

05:26.030 --> 05:26.980
You're on prep duty.

05:33.900 --> 05:34.740
Here, Changyue.

05:38.230 --> 05:39.690
Why isn't Lifei out yet?

05:40.140 --> 05:40.540
Here.

05:40.830 --> 05:41.620
Thanks, Changyue.

05:41.910 --> 05:42.570
Is it tasty?

06:13.710 --> 06:16.370
First, a toast to Xiuyuan's recovery.

06:16.880 --> 06:18.860
And then to us driving Zong Quan away!

06:19.440 --> 06:20.100
Cheers!

06:20.440 --> 06:20.770
Yes!

06:21.350 --> 06:22.370
Oh, Lifei,

06:22.760 --> 06:23.740
you never told us

06:23.760 --> 06:25.420
how Zong Quan finally left.

06:29.790 --> 06:31.770
That was all thanks to our formation's power.

06:32.230 --> 06:33.130
Besides,

06:34.830 --> 06:36.810
if he stayed, he would've been caught by the masters.

06:53.910 --> 06:56.300
You just recovered. You can't drink.

06:57.470 --> 06:57.810
I...

06:59.230 --> 07:00.210
Let me drink for you.

07:19.150 --> 07:20.010
Ye, Changyue.

07:20.470 --> 07:22.210
Looks like we'll have to drink more.

07:23.640 --> 07:25.130
You're keeping such good wine to yourselves.

07:25.440 --> 07:26.420
- Give it to me. - No!

07:26.760 --> 07:27.660
You can't drink.

07:27.680 --> 07:28.300
Why can't I?

07:28.320 --> 07:29.370
Changyue, let's have more.

07:29.830 --> 07:30.500
Give it to me.

07:30.520 --> 07:31.540
You can't have it.

07:31.680 --> 07:32.570
Just a little.

07:34.120 --> 07:34.940
Just pour me one cup.

07:34.960 --> 07:35.980
One cup, alright?

07:39.440 --> 07:40.130
So beautiful.

07:48.960 --> 07:49.690
Hey,

07:50.230 --> 07:52.500
they say making a wish to the moon really works.

07:52.680 --> 07:53.180
They'll

07:53.200 --> 07:54.890
deliver your wish paper to the moon.

07:55.000 --> 07:55.810
Let's write ours first.

07:58.270 --> 07:59.100
Really?

07:59.350 --> 08:00.940
For real. Try it.

08:02.910 --> 08:03.420
Just try.

08:46.470 --> 08:48.900
"May we be together forever."

08:51.200 --> 08:53.540
"The same every year."

08:56.660 --> 08:59.300
You two even wrote the same wish.

09:12.470 --> 09:13.380
What did you write?

09:16.980 --> 09:17.850
It's a secret.

09:32.770 --> 09:35.760
[Lucky]

09:44.220 --> 09:45.020
Don't worry.

09:45.590 --> 09:47.780
Lu's bound to have good luck

09:47.820 --> 09:48.780
and a long life.

09:49.830 --> 09:50.730
Once you're fully healed,

09:50.980 --> 09:52.210
we'll go to Xingzheng Hall together.

09:52.940 --> 09:53.660
Together?

09:55.230 --> 09:55.970
Together.

09:56.110 --> 09:57.490
We'll take on Zhenyunzi together.

10:04.460 --> 10:05.490
We're no match for him.

10:06.820 --> 10:08.570
Xuanshanzi is an elder of Xingzheng Hall.

10:08.990 --> 10:10.490
If he helps,

10:11.220 --> 10:12.610
maybe we can force Zhenyunzi to release Lu.

10:12.630 --> 10:13.180
No.

10:20.990 --> 10:21.810
That'd drag you all into it.

10:22.350 --> 10:23.450
What are you saying?

10:23.870 --> 10:26.380
You can't always be a lone ranger in this world.

10:26.710 --> 10:28.490
It's good to have people

10:28.510 --> 10:29.210
you can lean on.

10:29.420 --> 10:30.300
If we help each other,

10:30.420 --> 10:31.330
we can get through anything.

10:31.630 --> 10:33.380
Right. Lifei's right.

10:36.710 --> 10:37.210
Lifei,

10:38.340 --> 10:39.060
why haven't you written yours yet?

10:39.630 --> 10:40.300
Me?

10:41.710 --> 10:42.540
I...

10:54.510 --> 10:55.300
What's that?

10:55.560 --> 10:56.540
It means reunion.

11:03.940 --> 11:07.140
I hope I find my master soon.

11:07.560 --> 11:08.420
I hope Xiuyuan

11:08.460 --> 11:10.060
reunites with Lu soon.

11:10.510 --> 11:12.540
And I hope you get everything you wish for.

11:14.750 --> 11:16.210
What are you three whispering about?

11:16.510 --> 11:19.180
You get your wishes, but what about us?

11:20.060 --> 11:22.900
Our hearts are as one.

11:24.180 --> 11:26.330
We'll never part.

11:44.870 --> 11:46.420
Quick, make your wish!

11:46.940 --> 11:47.380
Come on.

11:50.180 --> 11:50.660
Here.

11:51.470 --> 11:52.180
Aim it over there.

12:52.710 --> 12:54.060
Hangover pill. Take it.

13:06.870 --> 13:08.260
I haven't seen you this happy

13:09.590 --> 13:12.060
since we left Gaolu.

13:18.160 --> 13:20.140
I made this. For you.

13:28.750 --> 13:29.810
I already have plenty.

13:30.040 --> 13:31.330
Give this one to Gelin.

13:36.040 --> 13:38.900
Do you remember when I first gave you

13:41.080 --> 13:41.900
a grasshopper?

13:45.920 --> 13:48.420
It's been eleven years already.

13:50.280 --> 13:50.810
Changyue,

13:53.700 --> 13:56.260
let me take care of you from now on.

14:09.280 --> 14:10.210
You're the Crown Prince.

14:10.710 --> 14:13.490
The Baili family has always been loyal to the Gaolu imperial family.

14:13.510 --> 14:15.490
I don't want your loyalty. I want your...

14:15.660 --> 14:16.450
Enough, Ye!

14:23.400 --> 14:25.900
You'll always be my and Gelin's

14:26.230 --> 14:28.060
beloved cousin.

14:29.400 --> 14:30.060
Cousin?

14:30.470 --> 14:32.730
It's getting late. You should head back and rest.

14:35.630 --> 14:36.260
Cousin?

14:37.080 --> 14:38.450
You only see me as a cousin?

14:39.080 --> 14:39.810
Can't you see

14:39.830 --> 14:40.730
how I feel about you?

14:44.320 --> 14:46.090
It's because of Gelin, isn't it?

14:46.870 --> 14:47.570
Is it because of Gelin?

14:48.040 --> 14:49.140
Is it because you care about Gelin?

14:49.280 --> 14:50.060
You're drunk.

14:50.080 --> 14:51.300
- Is it because of Gelin? -Don't say anymore...

14:56.230 --> 14:56.850
Changyue!

15:09.560 --> 15:10.300
It doesn't matter.

15:11.440 --> 15:12.260
None of it matters.

15:14.200 --> 15:15.570
Only you matter to me.

15:49.590 --> 15:50.330
Xiaobangchui.

15:56.040 --> 15:56.690
Xiaobangchui.

16:27.040 --> 16:28.020
Xiuyuan.

16:38.590 --> 16:41.490
Lifei, you're drunk.

16:43.040 --> 16:43.780
Get some sleep.

16:45.120 --> 16:46.990
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

16:46.990 --> 16:47.810
Xiuyuan.

16:48.680 --> 16:50.880
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

16:51.230 --> 16:52.610
You're really good-looking.

16:53.440 --> 16:54.940
I've never seen you smile.

16:55.440 --> 16:56.690
Give me a smile.

16:56.690 --> 16:58.480
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

16:59.080 --> 17:00.600
♪No calamity can rival♪

17:01.000 --> 17:03.710
♪The lingering thread of a fragrance♪

17:03.710 --> 17:05.140
Come on, smile.

17:07.320 --> 17:07.940
Smile.

17:07.940 --> 17:09.510
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

17:09.510 --> 17:10.380
Smile.

17:10.420 --> 17:12.660
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

17:13.100 --> 17:15.400
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

17:15.400 --> 17:16.050
Stop it.

17:17.200 --> 17:17.730
I...

17:18.510 --> 17:19.820
You always look

17:19.840 --> 17:21.530
so troubled.

17:22.510 --> 17:24.180
I've never seen you genuinely smile.

17:24.180 --> 17:25.680
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

17:25.680 --> 17:26.450
Smile.

17:33.480 --> 17:36.480
♪With you, we melt into mist and haze♪

17:51.310 --> 17:52.940
If you don't smile,

17:53.310 --> 17:55.140
I'm not letting you go.

18:00.120 --> 18:03.460
♪I trade the highest heaven and endless clouds♪

18:04.200 --> 18:06.360
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

18:06.760 --> 18:10.160
♪Pierced by countless arrows, pain and illness pile on♪

18:10.480 --> 18:12.840
♪Yet I remain silent♪

18:13.760 --> 18:17.280
♪Deep love and long yearning, a kiss falls into a dream♪

18:17.880 --> 18:20.280
♪In the distant night, bitterness blooms♪

18:21.280 --> 18:22.680
♪The grand chapter is rewritten♪

18:23.160 --> 18:26.200
♪Startling the whole world♪

18:27.680 --> 18:31.280
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

18:32.040 --> 18:34.480
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

18:37.680 --> 18:39.690
So you can bite me, but I can't bite you?

18:41.710 --> 18:42.940
Since I bit you,

18:43.470 --> 18:45.660
you're mine from now on.

18:45.680 --> 18:48.080
♪Comes that one moment of defiance♪

18:48.400 --> 18:51.680
♪In the human world or above, like flowing water♪

18:52.440 --> 18:54.840
♪And falling petals♪

18:55.240 --> 18:59.600
♪Let this fleeting life be whatever it may♪

19:20.470 --> 19:21.050
Shanhua.

19:24.470 --> 19:25.290
Lei Xiuyuan.

19:25.940 --> 19:27.420
- Shanhua! - Shanhua's on the verge of death.

19:27.860 --> 19:29.490
Come see him one last time.

19:30.980 --> 19:32.730
His life is in your hands.

19:33.620 --> 19:34.490
Know that.

20:22.980 --> 20:26.100
Lime powder. Escape talismans.

20:26.550 --> 20:27.210
All set.

20:28.070 --> 20:29.530
Zhenyunzi is threatening you

20:29.550 --> 20:30.180
with Lu's life.

20:30.220 --> 20:32.100
And you're going alone? Walking to your death?

20:32.230 --> 20:33.100
How did you know?

20:33.710 --> 20:35.340
I overheard it when I woke up last night.

20:35.700 --> 20:37.100
Xiuyuan, you should've told us

20:37.120 --> 20:38.180
about this.

20:40.940 --> 20:42.860
Zhenyunzi's cultivation is even stronger than Zong Quan's.

20:43.180 --> 20:44.180
This trip is practically suicide.

20:45.120 --> 20:47.730
You don't have to risk yourselves for me.

20:48.310 --> 20:49.420
A real friend isn't afraid of that!

20:52.000 --> 20:53.410
Let's go together. Saving him is what matters.

20:53.520 --> 20:54.500
Enough with the chatter.

20:54.680 --> 20:55.050
Yeah.

20:55.680 --> 20:57.370
When we formed the Fragrance Bond, we swore to

20:57.640 --> 20:58.610
live and die together.

20:59.600 --> 21:01.500
A man of honor keeps his word.

21:11.640 --> 21:12.770
Once I save Shanhua,

21:14.070 --> 21:15.250
I'll repay you.

21:18.270 --> 21:18.940
Let's move!

21:42.340 --> 21:43.770
None of you

21:44.100 --> 21:45.290
says anything to my face.

21:45.600 --> 21:47.100
Always hiding things and making me worry.

21:48.920 --> 21:51.210
Gelin, actually...

21:51.340 --> 21:53.140
Whatever you want to do, just go do it.

21:54.510 --> 21:57.580
If you're happy, I'm happy.

22:01.470 --> 22:03.250
Alright. Let's head back to the academy.

22:03.400 --> 22:05.380
Gelin! Gelin!

22:05.640 --> 22:06.340
Gelin!

22:09.310 --> 22:10.010
Your Highness.

22:18.270 --> 22:21.340
Your Highness, the master has been waiting.

22:21.960 --> 22:22.580
Please, come in.

22:23.100 --> 22:23.730
After you.

22:30.340 --> 22:32.250
Why are you here? And dressed like that?

22:32.790 --> 22:33.940
The academy doesn't pay us.

22:33.960 --> 22:35.140
I can't just burn through my savings.

22:35.600 --> 22:36.860
Need to find a side job.

22:42.060 --> 22:44.020
[Xingzheng Hall]

22:48.840 --> 22:49.450
What's wrong?

23:00.030 --> 23:01.100
When I came over,

23:01.860 --> 23:03.580
I noticed a pavilion with strong spirit energy

23:04.030 --> 23:04.970
and a barrier around it.

23:05.790 --> 23:08.210
Maybe it's Zhenyunzi's place.

23:08.790 --> 23:09.730
I want to check it out.

23:10.270 --> 23:11.250
Then I'm coming with you.

23:11.470 --> 23:13.420
No. This is an immortal sect.

23:14.030 --> 23:16.290
And too many people will alert him.

23:17.100 --> 23:18.970
You said it yourself, this is an immortal sect.

23:19.160 --> 23:20.620
Zhenyunzi has deep cultivation.

23:21.030 --> 23:22.420
If I don't draw him away,

23:22.640 --> 23:23.900
you'll definitely get caught.

23:24.600 --> 23:25.420
I have a way

23:26.640 --> 23:27.900
to lure Zhenyunzi out.

23:35.840 --> 23:37.770
This is the layout of Xingzheng Hall's barriers.

23:38.640 --> 23:39.770
Be careful when you move around.

23:40.270 --> 23:41.690
Don't trigger anything.

23:42.470 --> 23:44.380
Zhenyunzi is very cunning.

23:44.550 --> 23:45.450
How are you going to draw him out?

23:48.710 --> 23:51.250
Persuade Xuanshanzi to host a banquet for Zhenyunzi

23:51.680 --> 23:52.860
and test his defenses.

24:04.960 --> 24:06.860
After repeated inspections, the academy masters

24:07.340 --> 24:09.050
determined that dark stone

24:09.340 --> 24:11.210
was just a piece from Divine Tree Island.

24:12.070 --> 24:13.730
But Zong Quan won't let it go.

24:13.960 --> 24:15.050
He keeps hunting for the Divine Tree.

24:15.680 --> 24:17.380
Knowing my identity,

24:17.400 --> 24:18.420
he still tried to kill me.

24:19.440 --> 24:21.660
He clearly has no regard for the Yue State

24:21.680 --> 24:22.530
or Xingzheng Hall.

24:22.710 --> 24:25.290
Your Highness, is this why

24:25.790 --> 24:26.970
you invited me over?

24:27.310 --> 24:31.050
Sir, I've learned that the Divine Tree's power is immense

24:31.270 --> 24:32.380
and not for one person alone.

24:33.510 --> 24:36.900
Why don't we join forces to find it and share what we gain?

24:37.270 --> 24:40.380
Once we find the Divine Tree, we can elevate Xingzheng Hall.

24:40.400 --> 24:42.450
Don't let Longming Sanctuary seize the opportunity.

24:45.230 --> 24:47.420
Xuanshanzi, what do you think?

24:47.750 --> 24:51.690
A catastrophe is coming. We should set aside our differences,

24:51.710 --> 24:55.010
find the Divine Tree, and stand against the Sea Calamity together.

25:02.070 --> 25:05.250
That guard looks unfamiliar.

25:10.790 --> 25:12.820
With Tongzhou's appearance-changing pill,

25:13.030 --> 25:15.490
that old guy shouldn't recognize me.

25:33.200 --> 25:34.010
Zhurong Stone?

25:35.030 --> 25:37.820
Xuanshanzi, why would you pass down

25:37.840 --> 25:38.800
Xingzheng Hall's supreme treasure

25:38.800 --> 25:40.580
to someone who hasn't even formally joined yet?

25:42.990 --> 25:46.140
Xingzheng Hall was founded by the Ji clan's ancestors

25:46.510 --> 25:49.490
and has been supported by the Yue State for centuries.

25:50.550 --> 25:53.180
Tongzhou has long been recorded as my disciple.

25:53.640 --> 25:55.770
Sir, you attacked my guard.

25:55.990 --> 25:56.860
What do you want?

25:57.270 --> 25:58.660
Her spirit power is masked.

25:59.440 --> 26:01.620
She's taken an appearance-changing pill.

26:02.470 --> 26:04.140
I just wanted to

26:04.160 --> 26:05.970
see her true face.

26:06.440 --> 26:07.450
What's wrong with that?

26:11.160 --> 26:12.050
It's very wrong.

26:12.750 --> 26:13.420
Because...

26:14.680 --> 26:15.860
Because she's my concubine.

26:18.880 --> 26:21.420
I don't want others to see her face.

26:23.990 --> 26:27.010
Your Highness, you're young and passionate.

26:27.550 --> 26:29.580
Just as one would expect of Xuanshanzi's disciple.

26:31.510 --> 26:34.380
It's natural for the young to be caught up

26:34.400 --> 26:35.380
in romance.

26:35.790 --> 26:37.770
Since she's Tongzhou's concubine,

26:38.510 --> 26:40.770
please let it go.

26:47.270 --> 26:48.940
Keep a close watch on that Lu guy.

26:49.550 --> 26:50.970
Don't let anything happen to him.

27:09.340 --> 27:10.380
It really is you.

27:10.960 --> 27:13.050
Since you used Jiang Lifei as bait,

27:13.340 --> 27:15.860
why not trade her for Lu Shanhua?

27:16.750 --> 27:18.770
Why go through all this distraction?

27:19.680 --> 27:22.210
Since you want to see him so badly, let's go.

27:24.310 --> 27:25.010
Shanhua.

27:32.230 --> 27:32.770
Shanhua!

27:41.880 --> 27:42.530
What happened to him?

27:43.710 --> 27:46.900
A vengeful spirit devoured his soul and shattered his heart meridians.

27:47.920 --> 27:50.450
If I hadn't been feeding him spirit power,

27:50.920 --> 27:52.580
he wouldn't have lasted this long.

27:52.990 --> 27:55.690
But his spirit root is already destroyed.

27:56.100 --> 27:57.970
Feeding him more spirit power won't help.

27:58.440 --> 28:00.940
Without the fox spirit's power,

28:01.680 --> 28:04.660
he probably won't make it through tonight.

28:05.100 --> 28:05.820
Tonight?

28:09.470 --> 28:13.100
Don't you want to rebuild his spirit root

28:13.750 --> 28:14.820
and save him?

28:20.680 --> 28:22.340
You went through all this trouble

28:23.270 --> 28:25.180
because you're afraid I'll hurt Xiaobangchui.

28:31.680 --> 28:34.690
Relax. I have no interest in her.

28:34.990 --> 28:35.970
And I mean her no harm.

28:41.230 --> 28:42.100
Once the fox spirit is forced out,

28:43.960 --> 28:45.100
will the host be unharmed?

28:45.400 --> 28:49.820
Of course. It will also rid her of a great danger.

28:50.640 --> 28:52.290
The fox spirit is a malevolent spirit.

28:52.470 --> 28:55.450
It's been living in her body, waiting for the chance to take over.

28:56.360 --> 28:57.620
Extracting the fox spirit

28:57.840 --> 28:59.770
saves Shanhua

29:00.230 --> 29:02.450
and frees Xiaobangchui from that crisis.

29:03.230 --> 29:04.660
Two birds with one stone.

29:06.120 --> 29:07.420
What are you hesitating for?

29:13.990 --> 29:14.580
Shanhua!

29:31.360 --> 29:31.940
Fine.

29:34.510 --> 29:35.340
I'll do it myself.

29:37.750 --> 29:40.660
No matter what happens, you're not to touch her.

30:03.550 --> 30:06.940
A vengeful spirit devoured his soul and shattered his heart meridians.

31:00.860 --> 31:02.970
Without the fox spirit's power,

31:03.470 --> 31:06.210
he probably won't make it through tonight.

31:25.660 --> 31:26.860
This is a forbidden book.

31:27.380 --> 31:28.690
When you were unconscious,

31:28.710 --> 31:30.340
Lifei wanted to take out her inner core to save you.

31:31.140 --> 31:33.820
But her cultivation is low, and she's not a spirit creature.

31:33.860 --> 31:34.660
She doesn't have one.

31:35.510 --> 31:36.770
She was desperate to save you.

31:37.070 --> 31:38.490
She would've given her life.

31:43.270 --> 31:46.620
A blood-bound covenant initiated by heart's blood.

31:48.620 --> 31:51.250
Transfer all injuries from the recipient to the caster.

31:53.660 --> 31:54.620
Transfer all injuries?

31:57.790 --> 31:59.100
Did you find a clue?

32:07.550 --> 32:10.010
I'm warning you, don't do anything on your own.

32:10.180 --> 32:11.340
We're in this together.

32:11.940 --> 32:14.490
Yeah. We beat Zong Quan together.

32:14.660 --> 32:15.620
We can handle Zhenyunzi too.

32:15.750 --> 32:17.620
As long as the three of us stick together, we'll get it done.

32:23.990 --> 32:25.140
You found Lu?

32:32.710 --> 32:34.250
I found a secret chamber in Xuanyin Pavilion.

32:35.030 --> 32:35.580
But

32:37.380 --> 32:38.180
I couldn't break the formation there.

32:39.620 --> 32:40.340
Why didn't you say so?

32:40.380 --> 32:41.900
We can give it a try together.

32:42.180 --> 32:42.730
Right.

32:42.990 --> 32:44.900
No time to waste. I'll go prepare now.

32:55.710 --> 32:57.340
Careful. Feels like a barrier.

33:31.420 --> 33:32.660
This isn't Xuanyin Pavilion.

33:34.220 --> 33:34.860
Where are we?

33:42.420 --> 33:43.250
Let's go further in.

34:04.140 --> 34:04.970
It's the Altar of Martyrs.

34:06.230 --> 34:07.140
After the Sea Calamity,

34:07.620 --> 34:10.100
Xingzheng Hall enshrined all the fallen elders

34:10.270 --> 34:11.420
and disciples here.

34:12.460 --> 34:13.780
I heard Xuanshanzi mention it before.

34:14.780 --> 34:16.090
But because the resentment here is too strong,

34:16.630 --> 34:18.860
Xuanshanzi and Zhenyunzi declared it forbidden ground.

34:20.030 --> 34:21.010
How did we end up here?

34:22.590 --> 34:23.860
And these skulls...?

34:26.460 --> 34:27.490
They're demon remains.

34:32.380 --> 34:34.610
Did Zhenyunzi hide Lu here?

34:37.300 --> 34:39.570
Let's split up and search. Stay alert.

35:38.960 --> 35:40.610
Lei Xiuyuan, what are you doing?

35:47.630 --> 35:48.340
Xiuyuan.

35:49.820 --> 35:50.780
What are you doing?

35:51.720 --> 35:54.820
Sorry. I just want Riyan.

36:11.510 --> 36:13.220
Xiuyuan, let go!

36:34.300 --> 36:36.340
Bear with it. It'll be over soon!

36:51.070 --> 36:52.010
Xiuyuan!

37:06.510 --> 37:08.170
Lei Xiuyuan!

37:23.720 --> 37:28.700
Xiuyuan! Xiuyuan! Let her go!

37:41.670 --> 37:42.490
Riyan!

37:43.300 --> 37:45.740
Is my spirit power too weak, and the technique incomplete,

37:46.460 --> 37:48.090
so I could only take on part of her pain?

37:49.070 --> 37:49.700
Lifei.

37:52.270 --> 37:55.960
♪The warmth within my arms♪

37:56.340 --> 37:59.380
♪I can no longer hold on to♪

37:59.680 --> 38:03.080
♪In the cold night, how can I♪

38:03.440 --> 38:05.800
♪Keep you warm until sunrise?♪

38:05.800 --> 38:06.780
Lifei!

38:07.080 --> 38:09.150
♪My heartbeat freezes♪

38:09.150 --> 38:10.860
Lifei, let him go!

38:12.110 --> 38:13.010
I don't want to hurt you.

38:13.720 --> 38:15.530
I won't! Shut up!

38:15.530 --> 38:17.400
♪Looking you in the eyes, I cannot♪

38:17.680 --> 38:20.360
♪Utter that line♪

38:20.360 --> 38:22.490
Hand me over. You still need to find your master.

38:22.510 --> 38:23.380
You can't die here.

38:23.990 --> 38:24.970
Shut up!

38:26.070 --> 38:27.490
You know Ganhua Realm.

38:28.240 --> 38:29.530
You must know my master.

38:29.630 --> 38:32.570
And you saved me before. I can't let you die.

38:32.570 --> 38:34.600
♪I still linger on♪

38:35.000 --> 38:38.440
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

38:38.460 --> 38:39.050
Lifei.

38:39.780 --> 38:40.940
Xiuyuan!

38:40.940 --> 38:42.600
♪But we thought nothing of it♪

38:42.920 --> 38:46.360
♪With a heartbroken cry♪

38:46.720 --> 38:49.840
♪I wish you well♪

38:50.760 --> 38:51.490
Lifei.

38:52.070 --> 38:52.940
Lei Xiuyuan,

38:53.630 --> 38:55.340
I won't give up even if it kills me.

38:57.440 --> 38:58.380
Lifei!

38:59.400 --> 39:03.720
♪Running relentlessly without regret♪

39:04.160 --> 39:08.400
♪The storm looms, yet the wind stand in its way♪

39:08.760 --> 39:11.600
♪A final farewell left on the cliff♪

39:11.920 --> 39:14.080
♪I'd shatter my soul♪

39:14.480 --> 39:17.920
♪To lay all your days in peace♪

39:17.920 --> 39:18.570
Lifei,

39:19.150 --> 39:20.300
I won't let you die.

39:21.360 --> 39:26.160
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

39:26.400 --> 39:28.280
♪I will level the seas and mountains♪

39:28.600 --> 39:32.880
♪Break the waves, no matter how mad it seems♪

39:33.200 --> 39:37.560
♪The storm looms, yet I stand in its way♪

39:37.920 --> 39:40.800
♪Torn inside, still I burn bright♪

39:41.120 --> 39:47.200
♪With the light from my fingertips, I build a paradise♪

39:47.920 --> 39:51.150
♪To wander with you♪

39:51.150 --> 39:51.820
Lifei!

40:12.420 --> 40:13.490
Zhenyunzi?

40:51.590 --> 40:52.820
You said you wouldn't touch her!

40:53.550 --> 40:56.490
What, just watching breaks your heart?

40:57.470 --> 40:59.260
You had been soft

40:59.630 --> 41:01.090
and refused to hand over the fox spirit.

41:01.380 --> 41:03.340
I might as well take it all by now.

41:29.820 --> 41:31.300
Let her go!

41:38.340 --> 41:39.090
Lifei.

41:39.460 --> 41:40.490
Riyan!

41:44.780 --> 41:48.420
The spirit power of an ancient fox spirit is truly extraordinary.

41:48.780 --> 41:51.530
I finally have a chance to ascend to immortality!

42:05.720 --> 42:06.570
Lu.

42:37.900 --> 42:38.860
Riyan.

42:39.820 --> 42:41.130
Riyan!

42:42.200 --> 42:43.200
[The Eternal Fragrance]

42:43.200 --> 42:44.720
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

42:55.800 --> 42:59.480
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

42:59.800 --> 43:02.480
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

43:02.560 --> 43:05.800
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

43:05.800 --> 43:09.080
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

43:09.200 --> 43:13.080
♪Obsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise♪

43:13.360 --> 43:16.560
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

43:16.720 --> 43:22.800
♪No calamity can rival the lingering thread of a fragrance♪

43:23.080 --> 43:27.200
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

43:27.480 --> 43:30.160
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

43:30.360 --> 43:32.280
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

43:32.400 --> 43:36.720
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

43:36.880 --> 43:40.720
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

43:41.080 --> 43:44.080
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

43:44.160 --> 43:50.280
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

43:50.480 --> 43:54.200
♪With you, we melt into mist and haze♪

44:07.440 --> 44:11.200
♪I trade the highest heaven and endless clouds♪

44:11.400 --> 44:14.200
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

44:14.280 --> 44:17.680
♪Pierced by countless arrows, pain and illness pile on♪

44:17.680 --> 44:21.000
♪Yet I remain silent♪

44:21.160 --> 44:25.000
♪Deep love and long yearning, a kiss falls into a dream♪

44:25.160 --> 44:28.360
♪In the distant night, bitterness blooms♪

44:28.600 --> 44:34.440
♪The grand chapter is rewritten, startling the whole world♪

44:35.000 --> 44:38.920
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

44:39.200 --> 44:41.960
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

44:42.160 --> 44:44.000
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

44:44.160 --> 44:48.360
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

44:48.600 --> 44:52.480
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

44:52.720 --> 44:55.760
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

44:55.960 --> 45:02.680
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

45:02.720 --> 45:06.680
♪If the seal can't be broken, then let it go♪

45:06.920 --> 45:09.680
♪Where the heart finds peace, there is home♪

45:09.800 --> 45:11.720
♪Side by side, we fly through seas of clouds♪

45:11.880 --> 45:16.160
♪Break through the waves, the heart's ocean knows no shore♪

45:16.360 --> 45:20.200
♪Always, at the very end of fate♪

45:20.440 --> 45:23.560
♪Comes that one moment of defiance♪

45:23.600 --> 45:29.600
♪In the human world or above, like flowing water and falling petals♪

45:30.000 --> 45:34.360
♪Let this fleeting life be whatever it may♪
